Package com.garmin.android.connectiq

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ConnectIQ.ConnectIQListener
    Interface for receiving callbacks from various asynchronous API calls related to SDK initialization.
    ConnectIQ.IQApplicationEventListener
    Interface for receiving callbacks related to a specific application on a specific device.
    ConnectIQ.IQApplicationInfoListener
    Interface for receiving callback related to getApplicationInfo requests.
    ConnectIQ.IQDeviceEventListener
    Interface for receiving callbacks related to a specific device.
    ConnectIQ.IQSendImageListener  
    ConnectIQ.IQSendMessageListener
    Interface for receiving callbacks when sending a message or image to a Connect IQ device.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ConnectIQ
    This class is the primary interface for the Connect IQ mobile SDK.
    ConnectIQAdbStrategy
    ConnectIQ class for using an Android device to communicate with the Connect IQ simulator over ADB.
    ConnectIQDeviceStrategy
    ConnectIQ class for communicating with a device over BLE or with the simulator over BLE.
    IQApp
    Representation of a Connect IQ Application.
    IQDevice
    Representation of a Connect IQ device.
  • Enum Summary

    Enumeration identifying the various connection types supported by the SDK
    ConnectIQ.IQMessageStatus
    Enumeration returned from sendMessage() or provided when a message is received from a Connect IQ device.
    ConnectIQ.IQSdkErrorStatus
    Enumeration of values returned from initialize()
    IQApp.IQAppStatus  
    IQDevice.IQDeviceStatus
    Enumeration of possible device statuses.
